WEBVTT

00:00:00.708 --> 00:00:01.976
[Oliver Jeffers]

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:03.833
[Oda životu na Zemlji]

00:00:05.333 --> 00:00:06.601
Hej.

00:00:06.625 --> 00:00:09.601
Siguran sam da ćete do kraja rečenice,

00:00:09.625 --> 00:00:11.101
s obzirom na to kako govorim,

00:00:11.125 --> 00:00:13.976
svi već shvatiti da sam iz mjesta zvanog

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.268
planet Zemlja.

00:00:15.292 --> 00:00:17.018
Zemlja je baš sjajna.

00:00:17.042 --> 00:00:18.875
Ona nam je dom.

00:00:20.125 --> 00:00:21.393
I mikrobima.

00:00:21.417 --> 00:00:23.726
Ovi su k*** za sada u drugom planu,

00:00:23.750 --> 00:00:25.536
ali vjerovali ili ne, nisu jedini.

00:00:25.536 --> 00:00:29.393
Ovaj je planet također dom
automobilima, prokulicama;

00:00:29.417 --> 00:00:31.888
onim čudnim ribama
koje imaju vlastite čeone lampe;